    {
      "para_id": "Q000932.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Kindazid , his master , Ninkagina , child of Kakug , dedicated this ( mace ) for the well-being of Nammaḫni , ruler of Lagaš , and also for her own well-being . The name of this mace is “My master will rise , may he also raise him with himself!” ."
    }
  ],
